<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>彭博加密货币</title><link>https://bloomberg.com/crypto/</link><description>彭博加密货币</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 03 Mar 2026 12:32:01 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>欧洲央行文件警告称，稳定币可能对货币政策构成重大风险</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-03/stablecoins-could-pose-major-risks-to-monetary-policy-ecb-paper</link><description>欧洲央行发布的一份工作文件警告称，稳定币的广泛采用将对欧元区银行和欧洲央行的货币主权构成重大风险，特别是与美元等外币挂钩时。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iyn1khea7JJk/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Mar 2026 11:30:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-03/stablecoins-could-pose-major-risks-to-monetary-policy-ecb-paper</guid></item><item><title>由于长期伊朗战争的风险给加密货币带来压力，比特币暴跌</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-03/bitcoin-btc-slide-starts-anew-as-iran-uncertainty-drags-on</link><description>由于对中东长期冲突的担忧，比特币与其他风险资产一起下跌，抹去了 70,000 美元上方的短暂涨幅。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ioDoooC3HqMo/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Mar 2026 08:10:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-03/bitcoin-btc-slide-starts-anew-as-iran-uncertainty-drags-on</guid></item><item><title>加密货币的 24 小时承诺受到地缘政治现实检验</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-02/crypto-s-24-hour-promise-gets-a-geopolitical-reality-check</link><description>长期以来，比特币一直被宣传为提供其他市场无法提供的东西：24 小时实时了解全球风险。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i4AG3wmEmoho/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 02 Mar 2026 17:34:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-02/crypto-s-24-hour-promise-gets-a-geopolitical-reality-check</guid></item><item><title>随着市场波动加剧，比特币涨至 70,000 美元</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-02/bitcoin-advances-toward-70-000-as-volatility-increases</link><description>随着中东战争不断升级，全球金融市场波动性加剧，比特币推向近期交易区间的上限。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ifHg170SjOsQ/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 02 Mar 2026 16:00:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-02/bitcoin-advances-toward-70-000-as-volatility-increases</guid></item><item><title>银行监管机构采取措施限制美国稳定币奖励</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-02-26/federal-bank-regulator-moves-to-restrict-us-stablecoin-rewards</link><description>美国货币监理署提出规则，限制公司通过白标平台推出品牌稳定币并提供与之相关的奖励，这是该机构为实施唐纳德·特朗普总统于 7 月签署的联邦加密货币法的首次重大尝试。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iF__U9SRvdHk/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 26 Feb 2026 22:46:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-02-26/federal-bank-regulator-moves-to-restrict-us-stablecoin-rewards</guid></item><item><title>稳定币发行人 Tether 使用德勤提供 USAT 储备报告</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-02/stablecoin-issuer-tether-uses-deloitte-for-usat-reserve-report</link><description>多年来，Tether Holdings SA 一直表示主要会计师事务所不愿意提供审计服务，但现在，Tether Holdings SA 收到了德勤对其 USAT 稳定币有史以来第一份准备金报告的认可​​，该报告是为了遵守美国新法规而推出的。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/igbJWXXDFJAo/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 02 Mar 2026 20:14:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-02/stablecoin-issuer-tether-uses-deloitte-for-usat-reserve-report</guid></item><item><title>Saylor 的策略通过使用普通股加大比特币购买力度</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-02/saylor-s-strategy-mstr-steps-up-bitcoin-btc-buys-by-using-common-shares</link><description>Michael Saylor 的 Strategy Inc. 购买了价值超过 2 亿美元的比特币，并转向普通股为其大部分收购提供资金，尽管承诺将依靠其永久优先股。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ie1Zx_V76eOQ/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 02 Mar 2026 15:32:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-02/saylor-s-strategy-mstr-steps-up-bitcoin-btc-buys-by-using-common-shares</guid></item><item><title>由于油价预示着风险，加密货币交易者感到提心吊胆</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-02/crypto-traders-on-tenterhooks-as-oil-prices-signal-risks</link><description>随着美国市场在中东爆炸事件后重新开放，数字资产交易谨慎，交易员关注石油、股票和货币的连锁反应。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/irLFdjIcn3HI/v2/1200x-1.png" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 02 Mar 2026 03:23:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-02/crypto-traders-on-tenterhooks-as-oil-prices-signal-risks</guid></item><item><title>伊朗袭击引发不确定性，加密货币面临压力</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-01/bitcoin-btc-recovery-looks-tepid-as-iran-strikes-stir-uncertainty</link><description>周末美国和以色列对伊朗的袭击动摇了投资者的信心，导致加密货币面临压力，交易者等待全球传统市场的指示。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i9yiM3Ul6pt0/v3/1200x-1.png" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 01 Mar 2026 07:50:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-01/bitcoin-btc-recovery-looks-tepid-as-iran-strikes-stir-uncertainty</guid></item></channel></rss>